      "updated": 1783259246662,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "APIs Design\n(user id is part of the header extracted from auth token by the API Gateway\n\nGET /sessions/active -> session\nPOST /sessions {transactionId} -> {sessionId, status}\nPOST /sessions/{id}/messages {text|file} -> {assistantReply}\nGET /sessions/{id} -> full state\nPOST /sessions/{id}/pause\nPOST /sessions/{id}/resume\n\n\nExsisting APIs\nGET /evidence-requirements?payment_purpose=REFUND\n→ [evidenceType, kind, required]\nPOST /cases\nPOST /cases/{caseId}/evidence\n",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "APIs Design\n(user id is part of the header extracted from auth token by the API Gateway\n\nGET /sessions/active -> session\nPOST /sessions {transactionId} -> {sessionId, status}\nPOST /sessions/{id}/messages {text|file} -> {assistantReply}\nGET /sessions/{id} -> full state\nPOST /sessions/{id}/pause\nPOST /sessions/{id}/resume\n\n\nExsisting APIs\nGET /evidence-requirements?payment_purpose=REFUND\n→ [evidenceType, kind, required]\nPOST /cases\nPOST /cases/{caseId}/evidence\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
